      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This car has been meticulously kept in a climate-controlled environment, preserving the deep, mirror-like finish of the paint which is entirely free of rock chips, swirl marks, or blemishes. The interior is a pristine sanctuary; the premium leather remains supple with no bolster wear, and the cabin still retains its original factory scent. Every button, switch, and technological feature operates with tactile precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is immaculate, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule with a fully documented service history. The wheels are flawless with zero curb rash and are fitted with premium tires showing near-full tread. This is a rare opportunity to own a showroom-quality example that satisfies the most exacting standards.",
